WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.917
I fall upward through yesterday, wearing tomorrow like shattered glass.

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:11.700
Every clock blooms teeth and sings my name in reverse.

00:00:14.500 --> 00:00:18.917
The future remembers me before I learn how to vanish.

00:00:21.200 --> 00:00:25.700
Now is a corridor of mirrors drowning in unborn light.

